Why should you stay up to date with your #COVID19 vaccines?

Staying up to date with your COVID-19 vaccines lowers your risk of getting seriously ill, being hospitalized, or dying from COVID-19.

Find your vaccine or booster: https://t.co/xbvNibdkCt.

#DYK? Your body’s ability to fight off #COVID19 can decrease over time after vaccination. When this happens, a booster can help your body build back the immunity that has been lost.
